column5: https://www.foxnews.com/health/man-dies-from-extremely-rare-disease-after-eating-squirrel-brains  - boy between chronic waste disease in deer and this case  you wonder about eating wild animals anymore - we have CWD down here in certain counties in Pa. - if any deer showed up with this disease where I hunt I would propabably stop hunting deer
Well some people go to great lengths eating stuff I would shy away from.
Lol this title caught my eye...I'm sitting alone in a small corner Italian restaurant in lower Chicago thinking, this looks a scene from The Godfather. The foods great, but watch the door! Lol
just a horrible way to go...
